_header: O blessed Jesu high heavens king
_description: A prayer of confession — forty-three lines in couplets

HunEL34B7.First Lines:
O blessed ihesu hyghe heuens kyngeI moste Synfull creature of all
                    lyuyng…
HunEL34B7.Last Lines:
…O verey man that all thynge hathe wroghthaue mercy on me A
                    Synnar thowe hathe me deere boght
